JOHANNESBURG - The Gift of the Givers said they have received proof that kidnapped photojournalist, Shiraaz Mohamed, is still alive.
	
	Mohamed was kidnapped in Syria a year ago while accompanying the foundation. The foundation says the kidnappers sent a message in December claiming they knew his whereabouts. READ: SA journalist kidnapped in Syria It prepared a list of questions for Mohamed to answer to ensure his identity. Mohamed's family have confirmed that only Mohamed could know the answers to the questions asked. eNCA